citations:
    citation-asos-prologue:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Prologue"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Chett. Night's Watch at the Fist of the First Men. Chett plots a mutiny with Night's Watch deserters (Lark the Sisterman, Small Paul, Softfoot, Dirk, Sweet Donnel Hill, Sawwood, Maslyn, and others). Mormont assembles brothers to plan attack on wildling column. Three horn blasts signal the Others — wights attack the Fist."
